urls.description: The Environment Secretary George Eustice chaired a COBR meeting on the response to Storm Christoph this evening.

tweets.text:
A day of mixed emotions.
Floods can be devastating, & it's heartbreaking to see the lives & livelihoods affected by #StormChristoph. 
But I'm also immensely proud of how @EnvAgency colleagues, our partners & local communities are responding to the #flooding & reducing the risk. https://t.co/AimWQSovDo
